三、教學目標 Objectives


一 欣賞各國職棒比賽二 欣賞棒球文學電影三 體驗及實際參與棒球比賽四 學習及辦理校內棒球比賽1.Enjoying the baseball games in Various countries. 2.Enjoying the movies of baseball literary. 3.Haveing a experience and participate in baseball actualy. 4.Learning and carring on the baseball game in school. 





